For the purposes of this example however, we will run Shellter in Auto mode by selecting A at the prompt.

Next, we must select a target PE. Shellter will analyze and alter the execution flow to inject and execute our payload. For this example, we will use the Windows 32-bit trial executable installer for the popular music player Spotify as our target PE. The file is provided in the Resource section.

